  <static seed="603" source="Contrib/PCC/BasicAlgebra/PolynomialMultiplication/PolynomialMultiplication35.pg">
    <statement><p>Multiply the polynomials.</p>
<p><m>\left({t+5}\right)\left({t-9}\right)=</m><fillin characters="32" name="AnSwEr0001"/></p>
</statement>
    <answer>
      <p>
        <m>t^{2}-4t-45</m>
      </p>
    </answer>
    <solution><p>We use the FOIL technique- <alert>F</alert>irst <alert>O</alert>utside <alert>I</alert>nside <alert>L</alert>ast</p>
<p><m>\begin{aligned}
              \left({t+5}\right)({t-9})\amp ={t^{2}-9t+5t-45}\\
                                \amp ={t^{2}-4t-45}
      \end{aligned}</m></p>
</solution>
